'''La French Touch Conference'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rudebaguette.com/2014/06/24/la-frenchtouch-conference/|title=What is the point of La FrenchTouch Conference?|date=24 June 2014|website=rudebaguette.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/sparknews/bringing-a-french-touch-t_b_10476598.html|title=Bringing A French Touch To Business In New York|first=|last=Sparknews|date=17 June 2016|website=huffingtonpost.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> is an itinerant business event for [[entrepreneur]]s, [[investors]], [[corporates]], and members of the creative industries. It aims to promote French entrepreneurship abroad,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gouvernement.fr/en/la-french-tech|title=La French Tech|website=Gouvernement.fr|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lafrenchtech.com/actualite/la-french-touch-conference|title=La French Touch Conference|website=La French Tech|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> and was founded in 2014 by French entrepreneurs Gaël Duval & Cédric Giorgi.<ref name="lafrenchtech.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.lafrenchtech.com/agenda/la-french-touch-conference-paris-2017|title=La French Touch Conference Paris 2017|website=La French Tech|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://cnnumerique.fr/le-conseil/qui-sommes-nous/duval-gael|title=DUVAL - CNNum - Traducteur et éclaireur des transformations numériques|website=cnnumerique.fr|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> A total of seven editions were organized in [[Paris]],<ref name="lafrenchtech.com"/> [[San Francisco]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lafrenchtech.com/actualite/la-french-touch-unconference-san-francisco-2017|title=La French Touch &quot;Unconference&quot; San Francisco 2017|website=La French Tech|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> and [[New York City]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/axa-is-headline-sponsor-of-la-french-touch-conference-2014-06-19|title=AXA is Headline Sponsor of La French Touch Conference|website=marketwatch.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20150626-france-startups-new-york-contest-la-french-touch-pitch-conference|title=The French startups vying to conquer New York - France 24|date=26 June 2015|website=france24.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> Some of the past speakers hosted at the events include [[Yann LeCun]],<ref name="programme">{{cite web|url=https://frenchmorning.com/french-touch-conference-programme/|title=Emmanuel Macron à la French Touch Conference à New York - French Morning|first=Emmanuelle|last=Drouineau|date=15 June 2015|website=frenchmorning.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> [[Eric Hippeau]],<ref name="programme"/> [[Rachel Haot]],<ref name="maddyness.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.maddyness.com/evenement/la-french-touch-conference-new-york-city/|title=La French Touch Conference New York City - Maddyness - Le Magazine des Startups Françaises|website=maddyness.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> [[Alexandre Mars]],<ref name="programme"/> the writer [[Harlan Coben]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.faccsf.com/events/events-calendar/events/d/la-french-touch-conference-nyc/|title=La French Touch Conference NYC - FACC SAN FRANCISCO|website=www.faccsf.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.capgemini.com/fr-fr/news/la-troisieme-edition-de-la-french-touch-conference-reussit-son-pari-de-construire-le-pont-entre/|title=La troisième édition de La French Touch Conference réussit son pari de construire le pont entre les écosystèmes français et américain|date=29 June 2016|website=capgemini.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> the French designer [[Ora-Ito]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://americanentrepreneurship.com/ny/technology-news/axa-sponsors-2nd-annual-la-french-touch-conference-in-nyc.html|title=AXA Sponsors 2nd Annual La French Touch Conference in NYC|first=|last=AEP|website=americanentrepreneurship.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20150617006120/en/AXA-Sponsors-La-French-Touch-Conference-Promoting|title=AXA Sponsors La French Touch Conference Promoting Digital Innovation and Entrepreneurship between France and the US|website=businesswire.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> and the pastry chef [[Dominique Ansel]].<ref name="lesechos.fr">{{cite web|url=https://business.lesechos.fr/entrepreneurs/internationaliser-exporter/la-french-touch-embarque-les-start-up-de-la-tech-a-new-york-62793.php|title=La French Touch embarque les start-up de la tech à New-York - Les Echos|website=business.lesechos.fr|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref>
La French Touch Conference has been supported by the French government and the city of New York during its previous events, having hosted: * [[Emmanuel Macron]],<ref name="programme"/> then [[French Ministry for the Economy and Finance|Minister of the Economy]], now [[President of France]] * [[Axelle Lemaire]],<ref name="programme"/> then French Secretary of State for Digital Affairs * [[Fleur Pellerin]],<ref name="lesechos.fr"/> then French Secretary of State for Foreign Trade * [[Mounir Mahjoubi]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ouest-france.fr/economie/entreprises/french-tech/la-french-touch-conference-l-appel-de-mounir-mahjoubi-aux-startuper-5101322|title=À la French Touch Conference, l’appel de Mounir Mahjoubi aux startuper|website=ouest-france.fr|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> French Secretary of State in Charge of Digital Affairs * Alicia Glen,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://business.lesechos.fr/entrepreneurs/actu/la-french-tech-a-new-york-211652.php|title=News from La French Tech à New York - Les Echos|website=business.lesechos.fr|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> Deputy Mayor of New York City * [[Gale Brewer]],<ref name="maddyness.com"/> President of the [[Manhattan]] Borough
In June 2016, La French Touch Conference launched a [[start-up]] competition which took place aboard an airplane, called "Pitch in the Plane".<ref name="venturebeat.com">{{cite web|url=https://venturebeat.com/2018/02/13/french-startups-using-word-pitch-accused-of-trademark-violation-by-maker-of-nations-most-infamous-dessert/|title=French startups using ‘pitch’ accused of trademark violation by maker of nation’s most infamous dessert|date=13 February 2018|website=venturebeat.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/shelliekarabell/2016/06/23/entrepreneurship-a-la-francais-money-mentoring-and-a-pitch-in-the-plane/2/#20cfe1886d7d|title=Entrepreneurship A La Francais: Money, Mentoring And A Pitch In The Plane|first=Shellie|last=Karabell|website=forbes.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> Two editions have been organized on Paris-New York commercial flights. The start-ups SkyLights and Mapwize won the competitions in 2016<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lesechos.fr/26/06/2017/lesechos.fr/030409850983_pitch-in-the-plane----un-concours-de-start-up-de-haut-vol.htm|title=Pitch In The Plane : un concours de start-up de haut vol - Les Echos|website=www.lesechos.fr|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> and 2017<ref>{{cite web|url=https://frenchtechhub.com/2017/07/mapwize-wins-pitch-plane-2017/|title=Mapwize wins "Pitch in the Plane" 2017 - French Tech Hub|date=11 July 2017|website=frenchtechhub.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> respectively. Among the jury members: [[VentureBeat]] European Correspondant Chris O’Brien,<ref name="venturebeat.com"/> [[Géraldine Le Meur]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usine-digitale.fr/article/pitch-in-the-plane-quand-les-start-upers-s-envoient-en-l-air-pour-mieux-pitcher.N558793|title=Pitch in the plane : quand les start-upers s'envoient en l'air... pour mieux pitcher|website=usine-digitale.fr|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> Olivier Mathiot<ref name="start-up">{{cite web|url=https://www.tourmag.com/Start-up-Skylights-remporte-le-Pitch-in-the-Plane-d-Openskies_a81414.html|title=Start-up : Skylights remporte le "Pitch in the Plane" d'Openskies|first=La|last=Rédaction|website=tourmag.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://bfmbusiness.bfmtv.com/mediaplayer/video/what-s-up-new-york-la-french-touch-conference-organise-un-pitch-in-the-plane-pour-sa-troisieme-edition-2106-836937.html|title=What's Up New York: la French Touch Conference organise un « pitch in the plane » pour sa troisième édition - 21/06|website=bfmtv.com|accessdate=4 May 2018}}</ref> and Paul-François Fournier<ref name="start-up"/>
